{"tid":1220885,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶) [是日笑話] 林鄭月娥：參透佛理即可學會放下執著","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:51:54.000Z","uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc07ffbc58899be8c67bea8e3d909f332fb1147c","tid":1220885,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1456077-20190505.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1456077-20190505.htm&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWLPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=5097c7a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1456077-20190505.htm&h=4df33dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1456077-20190505.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在佛誕祈福大會說，無論大家是否佛教徒，如能參透佛理，都可學懂放下執著，有所領悟。<br />\n<br />\n本身是天主教徒的林鄭月娥致辭時說，佛教是香港的主要宗教之一，義理重在修心和導人向善。每年佛誕均設有浴佛儀式，寓意以佛祖的智慧洗滌內心污垢，淨化心靈。每年這個時份，香港市民以至遊客均可放下工作、放鬆心情，參與各區的慶祝活動，同沾佛光。<br />\n<br />\n她說，適逢今年是中華人民共和國成立70周年，感謝籌備委員會為香港市民心安排連串的佛誕慶祝活動。<br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n<br />\n爲免影響時事台運作我就貼係吹水台"},{"pid":"ebacacf483bea6154f6176937df18c33c46398ce","tid":1220885,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一日淋病唔撤回 一日都未成功！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b0bccbafbcfbeaf0a7c9f1bee9ee1759b43129fa","tid":1220885,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebacacf483bea6154f6176937df18c33c46398ce","tid":1220885,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一日淋病唔撤回 一日都未成功！！！</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"佢唔識咩叫放下執着 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=